---
layout: layout.njk
pageTitle: Affiliate
currentPage: /affiliate/
---

<!-- ── PALETTE STRIP ── -->
<div class="palette-strip">
  <div class="ps" style="background:#0A1A30"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#152E5E"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#C4580A"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#D4920A"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#6ABAE0"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#2A9E6A"></div>
  <div class="ps" style="background:#F0E6D2"></div>
</div>

<!-- ── PAGE HERO ── -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <p class="page-hero-eyebrow">Phook Partners</p>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title">Earn with every<br><em>truth you share</em></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-sub">Three tiers. Three stages of growth. Rooted in the brand, rising in reach, radiant with truth — the dandelion in motion.</p>
</div>

<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->
<section class="section" style="background:var(--cream)">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">How It Works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simple. Honest. Generous.</h2>
    <div class="two-col" style="align-items:start">
      <div>
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">The Phook Partners programme is built on the same principle as the brand: what you release with intention returns transformed. Share Phook Theory with your community and earn a commission on every sale — automatically tracked through your personal affiliate link.</p>
        <p class="section-body">You grow with us. As your sales increase, your commission tier upgrades automatically — no applications, no negotiations. The Phook Partners programme rewards real results.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem">
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.25rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;flex-shrink:0">🔗</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.25rem">Get your unique link</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--smoke);line-height:1.65;opacity:0.75">Apply and receive your personal affiliate dashboard and tracking link.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.25rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;flex-shrink:0">📣</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.25rem">Share the truth</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--smoke);line-height:1.65;opacity:0.75">Use your link across social, email, podcast, or any platform — swipe copy and graphics included.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:1.25rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center">
          <div style="font-size:1.8rem;flex-shrink:0">💰</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.25rem">Earn on every sale</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--smoke);line-height:1.65;opacity:0.75">Commission paid monthly. Tier upgrades happen automatically as your numbers grow.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── TIERS ── -->
<section class="section affiliate">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">Commission Tiers</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three stages of growth</h2>
    <p class="section-body">Every partner starts Rooted. Every partner has the path to Radiant. Growth is automatic — your numbers do the work.</p>
    <div class="tier-grid">
      {% for tier in site.affiliate.tiers %}
      <div class="tier-card {{ tier.cardClass }}">
        <div class="tier-icon-wrap {{ tier.iconClass }}">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28"><text y="22" font-size="22">{{ tier.emoji }}</text></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-name">{{ tier.name }}</div>
        <div class="tier-label">{{ tier.label }}</div>
        <div class="tier-pct">{{ tier.pct }}<sup>%</sup></div>
        <p class="tier-desc">{{ tier.desc }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

